The paper discusses the influence of phase noise on a CO-OFDM system, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of FFT and IFFT techniques also suggests a focus on signal processing (cs.PF) and communication systems (cs.SI). Finally, the study of transmission distance and BER specifications could also fall under the category of optical networking (cs.OH).
